'''Jake Lloyd''' (born [[March 5]], [[1989]]) played nine-year-old [[Anakin Skywalker]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']] and provided the voice for Anakin in a number of ''[[Star Wars]]'' video games.

